Products.Name: Helga's Digestive Wellbeing Barley Wholemeal
Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Helga's Digestive Wellbeing Barley Wholemeal' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription:
Helga's Barley Wholemeal Wrap - lower in sodium (+40% less sodium than other leading brands compared to 620mg/100g average for 80% of the wraps market (January 2020), 3x the fibre and source of protein. Contains no artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.

Helga's bakers begin with care by selecting the best quality ingredients, those that bring out the best taste in each other.

NEW Helga's Digestive Wellbeing Wraps are baked with a unique blend of BARLEYmax barley and wholemeal wheat flour that delivers 3 times the fibre of Helga's White Wraps to support gut health (Helga's Digestive Wellbeing Barley, Wholemeal Wraps contains 9.4g/100g of fibre and Helga's White Wraps 2.4g/100g of fibre (January 2020)).

Each wrap contains a blend of fibres that help feed the good bacteria in your gut and help with digestion (BARLEYmax barley contains a range of prebiotic fibres, such as fructans, beta glucan and resistant starch to support digestive wellbeing. Consumed as part of a healthy varied diet containing 3g/day of fructans). Good digestion supports the absorption of nutrients from your food, which is important for overall health and wellbeing.

BARLEY Max is a barley wholegrain with prebiotic fibre.

50% of your wholegrain daily target intake (One serve (1 wrap) of Helga's Digestive Wellbeing Barley, Wholemeal Wraps contributes 50% towards the Grains & Legumes Nutrition Council 48g Whole Grain Daily Target Intake).

Products.RichDescription:
Helga’s Mixed Grain Wraps are thin, round and flat. They are 10 inches in diameter, a creamy brown colour with visible grains and brown scorched marks appearance. They are a very soft and pliable texture making it a multipurpose wrap.
Helga’s bakers begin with care by selecting the best quality ingredients, those that bring out the best taste in each other. From mixing, proving, pressing and baking, we allow their true flavours to shine through in our wraps.

WHY NOT TRY?
Fill wrap with your favourite roasted vegetables along with feta cheese and salad.

IT'S NOT JUST BREAD. IT'S HELGA'S®
MIXED GRAIN
- Lower in Sodium†
- Source of Fibre
- Source of Protein
- 65% of your Whole Grain Daily Target Intake^
- Suitable for Vegans
- No Artificial Colours, Flavours or Preservatives
- No Added Sugar
- Health Star Rating 3.5 and Health Star Rating Chart
†30% less sodium than other leading brands compared to 620mg/100g average for 80% of the wraps market (January 2020).
^One serve (1 wrap) of Helga's Mixed Grain Wraps contributes to 65% towards the Grains & Legumes Nutrition Council™ 48g Whole Grain Daily Target Intake.
